# Roblox Rewind

**Your Spotify Wrapped, but for Roblox spending.**

Roblox Rewind is a Chrome extension that analyzes your complete Roblox transaction history and creates a beautiful, shareable summary of your spending habits.

[![Chrome Web Store](https://img.shields.io/badge/Chrome%20Web%20Store-Install-brightgreen?logo=googlechrome&logoColor=white)](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/Roblox%20Rewind/cpajgohmdhddfdieelgpeifijhanbgmn)

---

## Features

- **Spending Analysis** - Real money spent, Robux purchased, Robux spent, Premium months
- **Player Classifications** - From "Window Shopper" to "Certified Whale" based on spending
- **Real-World Comparisons** - See what else you could've bought with that money
- **Visual Charts** - Yearly spending trends and category breakdowns
- **Purchase Breakdown** - Creator purchases vs Roblox official items
- **Membership Timeline** - Your Premium/Builders Club history
- **20+ Fun Facts** - Personalized insights about your spending habits
- **Shareable Images** - 4 beautiful themes to share your Rewind

---

## Privacy

Your data stays on your device. All processing happens locally in your browser.

[View Full Privacy Policy](https://github.com/Cosisety/Roblox-Rewind/blob/main/Privacy%20Policy)

